# Patch-Name: 0012-explicit-sync-libobs.patch
# Patch-Origin: Adapted from upstream OBS Studio commit 68ca91b21d5a621f3a40bfc3cd82f4206b3ec854 and PR #11708.
# Patch-Reason: Backport gs_sync_t and the Linux EGL syncobj plumbing required for PipeWire explicit synchronization.
# Patch-Risk: High. Extends libobs and libobs-opengl Linux rendering internals and links libdrm for syncobj support.

diff --git a/libobs-opengl/CMakeLists.txt b/libobs-opengl/CMakeLists.txt
index bb85d959d..ee329e1d3 100644
--- a/libobs-opengl/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/libobs-opengl/CMakeLists.txt
